msgid "Given serial does not belong to given user!"
msgstr "ເລກຊີຣຽນທີ່ໃຫ້ມາບໍ່ໄດ້ເປັນຂອງຜູ້ໃຊ້ທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້!"

#: api/validate.py:1013
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Unsupported token type '{token_type}' for authentication initialization!"
msgstr "ບໍ່ຮອງຮັບໂທເຄັນປະເພດ '{token_type}' ສຳລັບການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນ!"

#: api/lib/postpolicy.py:98
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"<--- Please describe your Problem in detail --->\n"
"\n"
"<--- Please provide as much additional information as possible --->\n"
"\n"
"privacyIDEA Version: {version}\n"
"Subscriber: {subscriber_name}\n"
"Subscriptions: {subscriptions}\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<--- ກະລຸນາອະທິບາຍບັນຫາຂອງທ່ານຢ່າງລະອຽດ --->\n"
"\n"
"<--- ກະລຸນາໃຫ້ຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມຫຼາຍເທົ່າທີ່ຈະຫຼາຍໄດ້ --->\n"
"\n"
"ເວີຊັນ privacyIDEA: {version}\n"
"ຜູ້ສະໝັກໃຊ້: {subscriber_name}\n"
"ການສະໝັກໃຊ້: {subscriptions}\n"

